cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "React Odontogram Modul"
abstract: >-
  An interactive, SVG-based dental odontogram (dental chart) editor for React
  and TypeScript. Supports multi-surface caries and filling charting, endodontic,
  prosthetic and periodontal states, FDI/Universal/Palmer tooth numbering,
  HL7 FHIR R4 export/import, optional ICDAS II caries scoring, and a user
  interface localized in eight languages.
version: 1.10.0
date-released: 2026-07-03
url: "https://react-odontogram-modul.vercel.app/"
repository-code: "https://github.com/ZoliQua/React-Odontogram-Modul"
license: MIT
